com.steelypip.powerups.hydranode

Interface MultiAttributes<Key extends java.lang.Comparable<Key>,Value>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Fusion, HydraNode<Key,AttrValue,Field,ChildValue>, HydraXML
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbsConstantFusion, ArrayFusion, BadFusion, BadHydraNode, BadHydraXML, BooleanFusion, EvolvingProxyFusion, FlexiFusion, FlexiHydraNode, FlexiHydraXML, FloatFusion, IntegerFusion, NullFusion, ObjectFusion, StringFusion

    public interface MultiAttributes<Key extends java.lang.Comparable<Key>,Value>
    A kind of multi-map where: - An entry is called an Attribute - the key part is called the Key - the value part is called the Value
